_YXY69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/22/E6/wKgED1xG2-CAY_4zABS_ErD_YXY69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/22/E6/wKgED1xG2-CAY_4zABS_ErD_YXY69.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"421851107\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a><span class=\"pic_tag\" style=\"margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;\"><a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5424032.html\" class=\"_j_anchor\" data-poiid=\"5424032\" target=\"_blank\" data-cs-p=\"ginfo_img_poi_new\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;\"><em class=\"house\" style=\"width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;\"></em>塔佩门</a></span></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"421851489\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">吃了饭我们去&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/5424032.html\" class=\"link _j_keyword_poi\" data-kw=\"塔佩门\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(77, 77, 77); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);\"