splay: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"436194109\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">旁边就是长江索道，可以坐索道直接去洪崖洞那边，但是我去的时候人太多了，不想排队，很早之前也坐过一次，就放弃了。它的票价是，单程20，往返30。<br/>按照规划，我想周五六点多洪崖洞那边肯定很堵，我就直接做的地铁，去了大剧院，准备从千厮门大桥步行至洪崖洞。<br/></p><p><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.mafengwo.cn/photo/10208/scenery_12001186/436198165.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7E/5C/wKgEaVx8k8CAdImLAAFfCkKowrs670.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7E/5C/wKgEaVx8k8CAdImLAAFfCkKowrs670.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90%7CimageMogr2%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-rt-src=\"https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s13/M00/7E/5C/wKgEaVx8k8CAdImLAAFfCkKowrs670.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F1360x%2Fstrip%2Fquality%2F90\" data-pid=\"436198165\" alt=\"\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; height: 375px; width: 473px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;\"/></a></p><p class=\"_j_note_content _j_seqitem\" data-seq=\"436198251\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-word; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;\">从大剧院直接往洪崖洞方向走，感受了一下&n